verses.roman:
ei kathā govinda jagadānandere kahila
mauna kari' rahila paṇḍita, kichu nā kahila

synonyms: ei kathā—this message; govinda—Govinda; jagadānandere kahila—informed Jagadānanda; mauna kari'-keeping silent; rahila—remained; paṇḍita—Jagadānanda Paṇḍita; kichu—anything; nā kahila—did not reply.
translation: When Govinda informed Jagadānanda Paṇḍita of this message, Jagadānanda remained silent, not saying even a word.
